memory.summarizer_summary:
To proceed with the scanning request on [Inkers.ai](https://www.inkers.ai), fill in the following form fields with valid details. Do not click the submit button after filling in the details.

*   **Enter your first name (Name\_First)**
*   **Enter your last name (Name\_Last)**
*   **Enter country code (PhoneNumber\_countrycodeval)**
*   **Enter your phone number (PhoneNumber\_countrycode)**
*   **Enter your organization name (SingleLine1)**
*   **Enter your email (Email)**
*   **Enter area to scan (sqft) (Number)**
*   **Date Input**
*   **Address Line 1 (Address\_AddressLine1)**
*   **Address Line 2 (Address\_AddressLine2)**
*   **City (Address\_City)**
*   **State/Region/Province (Address\_Region)**
*   **Postal / Zip Code (Address\_ZipCode)**
*   **Select Address Country (Address\_Country)**
*   **Any questions or concerns (MultiLine1)**
*   **Enter your name (name)**
*   **Enter your email (email)**

It is important to fill required fields for successful scan.
